6 AS INTRODUCED
7 An Act relating to landlord and tenant; enacting the
Anti-Fungi Act of 2025; amending 41 O.S. 2021,
8 Section 118, which relates to duties of landlord and
tenant; requiring certain repair to be made in a
9 timely manner; requiring treatment of premises when
mold is present; providing timeline for treatment;
10 providing penalties for violation; providing for
noncodification; and providing an effective date.
11
12
