14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law not to be
16 codified in the Oklahoma Statutes reads as follows:
17 This act shall be known and may be cited as the "Anti-Fungi Act
18 of 2025".
19 SECTION 2. AMENDATORY 41 O.S. 2021, Section 118, is
20 amended to read as follows:
21 Section 118. A. A landlord shall at all times during the
22 tenancy:
23
