1 1. Except in the case of a single-family residence, keep all
2 common areas of his the building, grounds, facilities and
3 appurtenances in a clean, safe and sanitary condition;
4 2. Make all repairs and do whatever is necessary to put and
5 keep the tenant's dwelling unit and premises in a fit and habitable
